role description
as part of the data monitoring and management group an integral delivery unit within the global clinical trial execution gcte organization the clinical data scientist is responsible for timely and high quality data management deliverable supporting the pfizer portfolio the cds senior manager delivers asset level information strategy and service for optimal use and reuse of internal and external information that will advance research development and commercialization of the pfizer portfolio and further precision medicine the clinical data scientist design develops and maintains key data management deliverable used to collect review monitor and ensure the integrity of clinical data oversees application of standard data review and query management and is accountable for quality study data set release and consistency in asset submission data
